                     <interp inst="t18460921-1982-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing 1 coat, value 15<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18460921-name-1187" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18460921-name-1187" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
